üèó ENJOYING OUR PRIVATE ACCESS TO THE ROOF OF ANGKOR WAT! One of the most special things about my tours to Cambodia is that my passangers have private access (which is forbidden to the general public)  to the scaffolding of Angkor Wat. We are also accompanied by the chief arqueologist in charge of Angkor Wat's restoration: Dr. Hans Leisen. From this vantage point, you can see the unique sight of Angkor's roofs, something that regular tourists don't get to experience. I met Dr. Leisen in 1994 and by then he had already spent years working on the temples' restoration ‚öí Hearing his stories about his work and the methods he uses is fascinating as he is, without a doubt, the üåè's leading expert on Angkot Wat. There is truly no better way to experience Angkot Wat. We all left with the burning desire to become archeologists!! üîé";}i:160;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:1;}i:161;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:1;}i:162;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEvJqBMgqjK";}i:163;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:238:"https://scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/118673185_780740585800440_3218999089815239066_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_ohc=C2BQrwpDOuQAX-DlJyU&oh=2527713ef0bc43fc617b8f1b69c37407&oe=5F7A8FB6";}i:164;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:5:"image";}i:165;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:38206049456;}i:166;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:167;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:168;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:169;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2391172118417863196";}i:170;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEvJl9rHXIc";}i:171;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599269951;}i:172;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:303:"Wake up every morning with the thought that something wonderful is about to happen
